    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recently serviced double-VANOS system and calibrated valve clearances. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is preserved with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain optimal geometry under load. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a dedicated driver\u2019s car, the performance envelope remains sharp, offering the visceral feedback and linear throttle response only individual throttle bodies can provide.",
