    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle offers a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains its original factory luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper, consistent with careful daily use. The alloy wheels are curb-rash free and wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery is in great shape, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the high-fidelity sound system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is solid\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and it recently passed a full safety inspection. I have kept a detailed log of all oil changes and scheduled maintenance, which will be provided to the buyer. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next owner.",
